snippet.title: Best VGM 1887 - 3D Dot Game Heroes - Passing Through The Forest
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 3
3D Dot Game Heroes (2010)
Passing Through The Forest
Shinji Hosoe, Ayako Saso, Yousuke Yasui, Shoichiro Sakamoto, Teruo Taniguchi, Takahiro Eguchi & Norihiro Furukawa
